                <note rend="inline" type="source">832.415/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-02-18T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 18, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>15. Brazilian Ambassador, by instructions, invites this Government to attend
                    Centennial Celebration September next at Rio de Janeiro.</p>
                <p>Cable whether this is distinct from Exposition, if so, advising Department fully
                    regarding it and of action you recommend.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Fletcher</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
